defaultIntroductiondefault&#xa0;
defaultThis note 
defaultis provided by the Chartered Institution of Highways and Transportation, a professional engineering institution with 
default12,000 
defaultmembers
default who work in the highways and transportation sector. CIHT members plan, design, build, operate and maintain transport systems
default and infrastructure, whilst respecting the imperatives of improving safety, ensuring economic competitiveness and minimising environmental impact.
default&#xa0;
defaultThis note is concerned with issues affecting the mobility of older people in isolated communities.
